sequenceDiagram
    participant C as AutoPolyVary controller
    participant M as PixelRadianMap
    participant R as Render executor
    participant F as JavaFX thread
    participant V as PolyVaryTask
    C->>M: set coordinate i
    C->>R: prepare redraw generation i
    R-->>F: completed images for i
    F->>F: reject if stale, else commit i
    F-->>C: afterCommit(i)
    C->>C: sample committed pixels and build candidates
    alt candidates exist
        C->>V: start exactly one task for i
        V-->>F: partial and terminal results
        F-->>C: advance once
    else no candidates
        C->>C: print zero-work status and advance once
    end
